<div class="sect2">
<h3 id="1500">2.11. Sending messages after purchase</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>An order is automatically created in plentymarkets after a customer has purchased an item on eBay. You can automatically send a confirmation to the customer when the order is created in plentymarkets:</p>
</div>
<div class="ulist">
<ul>
<li>
<p>By sending an email to the customer’s email address</p>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p><em>or</em></p>
</div>
<div class="ulist">
<ul>
<li>
<p>By sending a message to the customer’s eBay user account</p>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
