<li>
<p>Save (<span class="icon "><i class="psicon-save"></i></span>) the setting.</p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
</div><div class="tab-pane fade" id="automatic-message-to-ebay-user-account" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="automatic-message-to-ebay-user-account-tab">
<h5 id="_entering_texts_for_messages_after_purchase" class="discrete">Entering texts for messages after purchase:</h5>
<div class="olist arabic">
<ol class="arabic">
