Listing type <strong>fixed price</strong>: When the price changes, it is not automatically changed on the market. You have to update the price manually or carry out a stock synchronisation. The price on the market can also change after the stock is synchronised if the exchange rate changed.<br>
Listing type <strong>auction</strong>: The item price is used as the price for the <strong>Buy it now</strong> option.</p>
</div></div></td>
</tr>
<tr>
