<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div class="content"><div class="paragraph">
<p>Select a <a href="#5500">listing template</a>.<br>
Either select a listing template for which a market is defined or select a <strong>market</strong> and create the listing without a template for this market.</p>
</div></div></td>
</tr>
