<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div class="content"><div class="paragraph">
<p>The market listing ID.</p>
</div></div></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Process</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div class="content"><div class="paragraph">
<p>The process type. Possible process types are <strong>Start</strong>, <strong>Update</strong>, <strong>Relist</strong>, and <strong>Finish</strong>.</p>
</div></div></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Status</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div class="content"><div class="paragraph">
<p>The status of the process. Processes can have the statuses <strong>Planned</strong>, <strong>Started</strong>, and <strong>Completed</strong>.</p>
</div></div></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Created on</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div class="content"><div class="paragraph">
<p>Date on which the process was created.</p>
</div></div></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Started on</strong></p></td>
