<p>Date on which the process was actually started.</p>
</div></div></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Start date</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div class="content"><div class="paragraph">
