</div></div></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Completed on</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div class="content"><div class="paragraph">
<p>Date on which the process was completed.</p>
</div></div></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Delete</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div class="content"><div class="paragraph">
<p>Click on <strong>Delete</strong> (<span class="icon red"><i class="fa fa-minus-circle  "></i></span>) to end the process and thus cancel the process from being started.</p>
</div></div></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<div class="sect2">
<h3 id="5955">19.1. Searching for listing processes</h3>
