<p>Use the filters on the left-hand side of the <strong>Listings » Listing processes</strong> menu to further narrow down the search results and to search for specific processes. <a href="#filters-future-listings">Table 26</a> contains an overview of all available filters. Select one or more filters and click on <strong>Search</strong> (<span class="icon blue"><i class="fa fa-search  "></i></span>) to display the search results.</p>
</div>
