</li>
<li>
<p><strong>ItemListingHelperMarketLister</strong> (start, relist, check: listings)</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>ItemListingHelperMemberMessages</strong> (eBay messages)</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>ItemListingHelperSyncListingHistory</strong> (group function: active listings)</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>ItemListingExternalPriceUpdateController</strong> (price synchronization)</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>ItemListingMarketLister</strong> (future listings, relisted listings)</p>
</li>
