<p><strong>EbayMarkAsReceived</strong> (event procedure: accept return)</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>EbayMarkRefundSent</strong> (event procedure: marking eBay refunds as sent)</p>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Viewing the API log:</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
<ol class="arabic">
<li>
<p>Go to <strong>Data » API log » Tab: API log</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Select a format from the <strong>Process</strong> drop-down list.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong><em>Optional:</em></strong> Select a date if you only want to see entries for a specific day.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Select the number of results per page.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on <strong>Search</strong> (<span class="icon blue"><i class="fa fa-search  "></i></span>) to display the results.</p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
