</li>
<li>
<p>Click on the <strong>Other</strong> tab.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Select an account from the drop-down list.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on <strong>Start</strong> to import the shipping discounts for combined payments.<br>
→ Your eBay account information is transferred to plentymarkets.</p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
